      <h1 class='title'>Military Airfields</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 08 January 2003 vol 397 c224WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_224ws' title='Col. 224WS &mdash; HC Deb 08 January 2003 vol 397 c224WS' name='column_224ws' href='#column_224ws' rel='bookmark'>224WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0397P0-05988'>
        <a name='S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_75'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-david-drew' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_75' title='Link to this speech by Mr David Drew' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-david-drew" title="Mr David Drew">Mr. Drew</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0397P0-05988">To ask the Secretary of State for Defence what liaison takes place between his Department and<span class="italic">(a)</span> local hon. Members and <span class="italic">(b)</span> local authorities in the use of domestic military airfields when being used by the aircraft of a foreign power. [88321]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0397P0-05989'>
        <a name='S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_76'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-adam-ingram' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_76' title='Link to this speech by Mr Adam Ingram' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-adam-ingram" title="Mr Adam Ingram">Mr. Ingram</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0397P0-05989">Regular liaison takes place between RAF stations and local authorities. This includes notification of foreign aircraft activity, where it varies from the routine.</p><p id="S6CV0397P0-05990">Members of Parliament are similarly advised of such non-routine activity by either my hon. Friend the Parliamentary Under Secretary of State for Defence or myself.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
